    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天使降临，暴力福音</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果施主看不懂《圣经》，那么天使也略懂一些火力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《物理超度指南》是一款融合了物理破坏、肉鸽玩法与暴力射击的俯视角射击爽游。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个善良的天使，你眼中容不得罪恶。你的降临，便是为了用最纯粹的力量，把地狱超度成你的伊甸园！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别念经了，拿起家伙开炸吧——罪恶太多，必须物理超度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/c8d8dd401883ce4f4a4fb3e5b413e02b.poster.avif?t=1767975503\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/c8d8dd401883ce4f4a4fb3e5b413e02b.webm?t=1767975503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/c8d8dd401883ce4f4a4fb3e5b413e02b.mp4?t=1767975503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真·物理破坏系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有什么是你手中的武器解决不了的，如果有，那就再来一发核弹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >墙体能炸、地形可毁、怪物直接升天！ 你可以利用爆炸连锁反应，把成群的敌军炸得四分五裂。你也可以轰碎一整个掩体，将躲在后面的怪物一网打尽！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要你够狠，这世界就没有打不穿的墙，也没有杀不了的怪！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/8e3df0735198c577e7dafc4a2a3aee90.poster.avif?t=1767975503\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/8e3df0735198c577e7dafc4a2a3aee90.webm?t=1767975503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/8e3df0735198c577e7dafc4a2a3aee90.mp4?t=1767975503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扳机，是天使的外交手段</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《物理超度指南》里，你可以自由选择使用哪种方式升天对手。火力清单从现实到神圣，从现代战术到超自然裁决，你手里有的是大杀器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用核弹清场，让激光贯穿一切，用火焰喷射器横扫所有不服！RPG炸碎障碍，狙击步枪不仅能精准狙杀，还能顺带清除后排的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里的每个 Boss 都蛮横不讲理，攻击花哨又硬核。如果火力不够，那就叠加技能，让下一发炮弹送它全家团灭！怪物敢藏身，就让掩体和它一起升天！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火力即正义，扳机即福音！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/4a112ea3d50c4500981ecc48ba58aa78.poster.avif?t=1767975503\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/4a112ea3d50c4500981ecc48ba58aa78.webm?t=1767975503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/4a112ea3d50c4500981ecc48ba58aa78.mp4?t=1767975503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现在不是讲道理的时候，是讲物理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >审判之日已至！时间差不多喽，该超度了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地狱还在嚣张，怪物还没闭嘴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那就别客气——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扛起火箭筒，架起狙击炮，把神圣之雨洒满整片战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是地狱爬出来的，还是天上漏下来的，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要站在你面前，都该接受火力的赎罪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为地狱的噩梦吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——愿弹药与你同在，阿门。</p>",
